{"id":78922,"title":"Auditory verbal therapy in the UK.","abstract":"Newborn Hearing Screening has changed the working environment for both users and providers of services for children with impaired hearing. There is increasing interest in Auditory Verbal Therapy (AVT), both from parents and from professionals seeking to improve their skills. This article outlines some of the key themes which are relevant to the practice and provision of AVT in the UK. ","date":"2014-02-18","categories":"Otorhinolaryngologic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24533754","annotations":[{"name":"Hearing (sense)","weight":0.655988,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hearing_(sense)"},{"name":"Hearing impairment","weight":0.603496,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hearing_impairment"},{"name":"Infant","weight":0.511634,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infant"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.268146,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Language","weight":0.054746,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language"},{"name":"United Kingdom","weight":0.0546925,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_Kingdom"},{"name":"Auditory system","weight":0.0522101,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Auditory_system"},{"name":"Screening (medicine)","weight":0.0300804,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Screening_(medicine)"},{"name":"Environment (biophysical)","weight":0.0279596,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Environment_(biophysical)"},{"name":"Slow-scan television","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Slow-scan_television"},{"name":"Key (lock)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Key_(lock)"},{"name":"Verbal (rapper)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Verbal_(rapper)"},{"name":"Theme (literature)","weight":0.0147415,"wikiped